---
title: Hello Hero: Creamy Beef & Pork Penne with Veggies
description: Both a beef and pork mince are cooked into a romesco creamy sauce dotted with pan-fried veggies for a rich and decadent
pasta sauce. Sprinkle with some Parmesan cheese at serving to add bite and a hint of nostalgia, because what pasta would be
complete without a little cheese.

*We’ve replaced the fusilli in this recipe with penne due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your
recipe card!*
